{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "24", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "07", "M": "46", "S": "05"}}, "news": [{"title": "After bulldozers, focus shifts to cleanup, road restoration and infra upgrade in Gurugram", "para": "Gurugram authorities are now clearing debris and restoring roads after demolishing encroachments. The Town and Country Planning department has directed developers and the Municipal Corporation of Gurugram to complete restoration work within 15 days. This move also paves the way for much-needed infrastructure upgrades in colonies. Residents are observing the progress, hoping for lasting improvements and no re-encroachment.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/gurugrams-recovery-cleanup-and-infrastructure-upgrades-after-demolitions/130482967?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-243408/130482967.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "MCM sets April 27 deadline for Manesar land survey", "para": "The Municipal Corporation of Manesar has set April 27 as the deadline for its digital land survey under the Centre\u2019s \u2018Naksha\u2019 project. This initiative aims to create a digital database of all land parcels, enhancing transparency and aiding in infrastructure development. Residents are urged to cooperate with survey teams to ensure accurate land records.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/deadline-set-for-digital-land-survey-completion-in-manesar/130482929?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-69374/130482929.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Mumbai: Dharavi residents to get 500-754 sq ft rehabilitation flats", "para": "Dharavi redevelopment project residents will now receive larger rehabilitation flats. The government has proposed a minimum of 500 sq ft carpet area, a significant increase from the previous offer. This change aims to benefit thousands of households. Residents await further details on relocation and the master plan.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/dharavi-redevelopment-project-residents-set-for-spacious-rehabilitation-flats/130482762?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-255226/130482762.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}]}